citations.desc: Access and inspection of records and property; submission of itineraries.
citations.narrative:
A responsible adult was not available to accompany APHIS Officials during the inspection process at 1:00 pm on
11/19/2025. Finding no one home, the inspector called the licensee's phone and left a message. The inspector then called
the licensee's family member and he said he would try to contact the licensee. Receiving no replies within 30 minutes, the
inspector left another message on the licensee's phone, left a note in the door of her home, and left the facility at 1:30pm..
Failure to provide access to the facility, animals, and records for inspection is a serious violation of the AWA and
regulations. Failure to comply may result in enforcement action.
End Section
